'''Bloah''' was a swear word used in [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]].<ref name="TGhost">''[[Tatooine Ghost]]''</ref> Could also be used as part of a longer interjection, e.g. "what the bloah is that?"<ref name="Joiner King" />

